RetroArch AI Translation Configuration on Android

To: Mr. Sims

From: Bryan Treanton

Step-by-Step Guide

Step 1: Create a ZTranslate Account

Navigate to ztranslate.net and create a free account. No credit card info required.

Step 2: Obtain Your API Key

Go to Settings in ZTranslate to get your API key.

Step 3: Configure AI Service in RetroArch

Open RetroArch and navigate to Settings → AI Service. Ensure AI Service is enabled. Then, enter the following in AI Service URL:

http://ztranslate.net/service?api_key=APIKEY

(Replace APIKEY with your personal API key.)

Step 4: Set Your Hotkey

Go to Settings → Input → Hotkeys. Scroll down to AI Service and choose a hotkey for translation.

Step 5: Save Your Configuration

Navigate back to the Main Menu → Configuration File. Choose 'Save Current Configuration' to keep your settings.
